      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-num                =    01
                     move  "N"            to   rr-snx-sdr
           else if   v-num                =    02
                     move  "S"            to   rr-snx-sdr
           else      move  spaces         to   rr-snx-sdr             .
